{"tid":1183462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海南廢除禁賭法規　惹鋪路開賭揣測","createTime":"2019-06-03T02:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T05:23:47.000Z","uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f83abd3d603aef2cfe8d786e83af677b924c51b5","tid":1183462,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海南省人大常委會前天通過，廢除包括禁止賭博、彩票罰款等地方法規，令人關注當地是否欲借積極發展旅遊業，將開內地先河營運合法博彩業。北京去年宣佈規劃建設海南自由貿易港，外界視此舉為中國應對中美貿易戰的舉措。<br />\n<br />\n《海南日報》昨報道，海南省人大常委會發出公告，宣佈自6月1日起通過廢除14項地方法規，包括《海南省禁止賭博規定》、《海南省取締賣淫嫖娼規定》以及《關於批准〈海南省彩票管理辦法〉設定罰款的決定》等。"},{"pid":"5dbf5172aec729387c053cfda053625fe25579ec","tid":1183462,"uid":254183,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:41:51.000Z","msg":"用海南取代香港澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a968ad14156eeb8ed8c24082b99c5d83e72689f5","tid":1183462,"uid":511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5dbf5172aec729387c053cfda053625fe25579ec","tid":1183462,"uid":254183,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:41:51.000Z","msg":"用海南取代香港澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"澳門人有福了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48cfdd1054f036f1600c10e13e45c3d49029b5b6","tid":1183462,"uid":50386,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:43:05.000Z","msg":"澳門已經冇利用價值<br />\n好快到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89935ea9b50add9d24eccaba03e8ca165bf781ed","tid":1183462,"uid":127108,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:44:09.000Z","msg":"係就仆街啦，澳門聽教聽話都比中共賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02d0c6c13923e7afbb0a92e45b69bb53a000877","tid":1183462,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco